title: H.G.Wells.The War of the Worlds.Multisound book.iso
description:
Description:
The world's first sound book. Enjoy full range sound effects while reading the book. This is an experimental project that we have started this project long ago and today we are happy to present it here. We strongly believe that this book will change the way people read the books. Your feedbacks are welcomed. 

Requirements:
Windows XP or Higher
Microsoft Net Framework 2.5 or higher
